For safe retraining, establish a gating pipeline: (1) offline validation on held-out data, (2) canary A/B test with statistical significance (p < 0.05), (3) gradual traffic ramp (10% → 50% → 100%) with automatic rollback triggers. Implement guardrails including: latency SLOs (p99 < 50ms), error rate limits (< 0.1%), and business metric floors (CTR cannot drop > 5%). Use exposure controls to cap new model exposure at 20% initially, with automatic rollback if guardrails breach.

